<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[make wontons: slowly sprinkle water in flour + baking powder, and work into dough]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[rest covered 1h]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[
process meat and ginger into a paste]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add the remaining ingredients and process some more]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[
roll out dough, cut in triangles and make wontons]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[cook in boiling water for 3 mins]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[put in soup bowls, together with julienne spring onions]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[
boil stock, put in soup ingredients,, cook 2 mins]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[pour over soup]]></step>
